description			"Hondo Ohnaka

Class: ARC Trooper
Brief Overview: 
A dexterous melee/gunner/pulse grenadier hybrid with a devastating shotgun. 

Weaponry:
- Modified E-5 Rifle (Based on Westar M5 level 1 w/scope attachment)
- ACP Array Gun *
- Cutlass *
- Pulse Grenades (3)

* Special Weapon Descriptions:
--- ACP Array Gun
- Based on Shotgun level 2
- Hitscan projectiles
- Pump Action (1 shot per clip)
- Magazine style reload

--- Cutlass
- Defense (1)
- Can use Yellow and Cyan styles
- Deals reduced damage
- Cannot block blaster fire
- Can block lightsabers

Attributes:
- Invisible to Force Sense
- Heal (2)

Abilities:
- Stamina (3) [Class Special 1]
- Dodge (3) [Class Special 1]
- Dexterity (3) [Alt Ability 1]
--- Grappling Hook (2)
- Hold Special Ability 2 while melee is equipped, then hold spacebar to ascend or crouch to descend"

Hondo Ohnaka was the leader of the Ohnaka Gang of space pirates during the Clone Wars. His gang was involved in trading spice and receiving ransoms through kidnapping."

